Peter Zellner is a researcher in the field of process optimization and data science for remote sensing applications at Eurac Research. 
This position allows him to combine his passion for the alpine environment and data science. 
Before he has worked at a the market research company GfK where he brought a spatial domain to market analysis. 
Throughout his career he relies on R as the major tool for creating solutions, be it process optimization, geoinforamtics or visualization of results.
